and thousands

00:12:20.350 --> 00:12:22.720 align:middle line:90%
of books written by the Maya.

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:28.310 align:middle line:84%
They destroyed them all, except
three books which have left.

00:12:28.310 --> 00:12:32.140 align:middle line:84%
Well, now just imagine in
our society, if for a war

00:12:32.140 --> 00:12:35.450 align:middle line:84%
or whatever, every Bible
would be destroyed,

00:12:35.450 --> 00:12:38.650 align:middle line:84%
but the priest and the
believers in Christianity,

00:12:38.650 --> 00:12:42.470 align:middle line:84%
they know the context of
the Bible in their brain.

00:12:42.470 --> 00:12:45.340 align:middle line:84%
So they start to
rewrite the Bible.

00:12:45.340 --> 00:12:47.710 align:middle line:84%
The same thing happened
in Central America.

00:12:47.710 --> 00:12:49.870 align:middle line:90%
All the books were destroyed.

00:12:49.870 --> 00:12:54.430 align:middle line:84%
The priests re-wrote
their old knowledge,

00:12:54.430 --> 00:12:57.680 align:middle line:84%
and so the Chilam
Balam book happened,

00:12:57.680 --> 00:13:00.190 align:middle line:84%
and in the Chilam Balam
book, one of the priests

00:13:00.190 --> 00:13:03.340 align:middle line:84%
explains why have
our forefathers

00:13:03.340 --> 00:13:08.380 align:middle line:84%
started the calendar of the
Maya on August 11, 3114 BC.

00:13:08.380 --> 00:13:11.580 align:middle line:84%
Because that was the
day when the Gods

00:13:11.580 --> 00:13:14.230 align:middle line:90%
descended from the firmament.

00:13:14.230 --> 00:13:17.830 align:middle line:90%
That was the starting point.

00:13:17.830 --> 00:13:20.220 align:middle line:90%
