but some of the cases

00:22:27.150 --> 00:22:28.750 align:middle line:90%
are very, very serious.

00:22:28.750 --> 00:22:30.460 align:middle line:84%
We should listen
to these people.

00:22:30.460 --> 00:22:32.470 align:middle line:84%
We should listen to
them what happened.

00:22:32.470 --> 00:22:35.438 align:middle line:90%
So we are under observation.

00:22:35.438 --> 00:22:41.790 align:middle line:90%


00:22:41.790 --> 00:22:46.070 align:middle line:10%
By the way, I myself
never saw a UFO.

00:22:46.070 --> 00:22:46.870 align:middle line:90%
I'm unhappy.

00:22:46.870 --> 00:22:49.420 align:middle line:90%
I would like a lot to see a UFO.

00:22:49.420 --> 00:22:53.450 align:middle line:84%
So these extraterrestrials,
if they are here,

00:22:53.450 --> 00:22:56.680 align:middle line:84%
they have a much more
advanced technology than we.

00:22:56.680 --> 00:22:59.080 align:middle line:84%
It would be no problem
for them to show up

00:22:59.080 --> 00:23:00.310 align:middle line:90%
in a football stadium.

00:23:00.310 --> 00:23:03.860 align:middle line:84%
The whole humanity would see,
hey, what's happening here?

00:23:03.860 --> 00:23:04.660 align:middle line:90%
There's a UFO.

00:23:04.660 --> 00:23:08.770 align:middle line:84%
Over 10,000 people
flying over the stadium.

00:23:08.770 --> 00:23:10.190 align:middle line:90%
They could do it.

00:23:10.190 --> 00:23:12.010 align:middle line:10%
Why do they not do it?

00:23:12.010 --> 00:23:14.560 align:middle line:84%
Because they know
how we function.

00:23:14.560 --> 00:23:15.880 align:middle line:90%
How we react.

00:23:15.880 --> 00:23:18.880 align:middle line:84%
If we are not prepared
for this event,

00:23:18.880 --> 00:23:20.680 align:middle line:90%
we would be completely shocked.

00:23:20.680 --> 00:23:22.880 align:middle line:90%
So we have to be prepared.

00:23:22.880 --> 00:23:24.700 align:middle line:90%
We have to lose our fear.

00:23:24.700 --> 00:23:27.850 align:middle line:84%
We have to understand they
are not here to kill us--

00:23:27.850 --> 00:23:29.030 align:middle line:90%
to destroy us.

00:23:29.030 --> 00:23:31.090 align:middle line:84%
They could have done
this for eternity.

00:23:31.090 --> 00:23:32.866 align:middle line:90%
They are here to help us.

00:23:32.866 --> 00:23:34.750 align:middle line:90%
To help us in what?

00:23:34.750 --> 00:23:37.420 align:middle line:90%
To help us in technology.

00:23:37.420 --> 00:23:40.410 align:middle line:84%
Today, we have a lot of
problems on our planet

00:23:40.410 --> 00:23:44.140 align:middle line:84%
with pollution, overpopulation,
world warming, climate,

00:23:44.140 --> 00:23:46.550 align:middle line:90%
all these things.

00:23:46.550 --> 00:23:50.560 align:middle line:84%
The extraterrestrials will
not solve our problem.

00:23:50.560 --> 00:23:53.920 align:middle line:84%
They had their own evolution,
and they had all these problems

00:23:53.920 --> 00:23:58.880 align:middle line:84%
at their home too, maybe
some 10,000 years ago.

00:23:58.880 --> 00:24:03.560 align:middle line:84%
They tell us what we must
do to solve these problems,

00:24:03.560 --> 00:24:05.591 align:middle line:90%
but we have to do it ourselves.

00:24:05.591 --> 00:24:14.740 align:middle line:90%


00:24:14.740 --> 00:24:18.100 align:middle line:84%
As every educated
person, I know we

00:24:18.100 --> 00:24:20.680 align:middle line:84%
are in the middle
of a climate change.

00:24:20.680 --> 00:24:22.000 align:middle line:90%
That's for sure.

00:24:22.000 --> 00:24:26.320 align:middle line:84%
No one can deny this,
but now whole humanity

00:24:26.320 --> 00:24:32.530 align:middle line:84%
is fighting against the
climate change by avoiding CO2.

00:24:32.530 --> 00:24:36.540 align:middle line:84%
But the problem is,
in antiquity, 7,000,

00:24:36.540 --> 00:24:40.190 align:middle line:84%
8,000 years ago, we had
already climate change.

00:24:40.190 --> 00:24:43.870 align:middle line:84%
This can be proven absolutely
clear because the glaciers went

00:24:43.870 --> 00:24:45.670 align:middle line:90%
back and the stones.

00:24:45.670 --> 00:24:50.590 align:middle line:84%
But some 8,000 years, there were
no humanity with industries,

00:24:50.590 --> 00:24:53.530 align:middle line:90%
with cars, who produced CO2.

00:24:53.530 --> 00:24:58.950 align:middle line:84%
So maybe we are on the wrong
track fighting against CO2,

00:24:58.950 --> 00:25:01.570 align:middle line:84%
hoping that this would
change our climate.

00:25:01.570 --> 00:25:04.180 align:middle line:84%
So we can ask the
extraterrestrials.

00:25:04.180 --> 00:25:06.740 align:middle line:84%
We have a problem,
climate change.

00:25:06.740 --> 00:25:09.340 align:middle line:84%
What can we do
against to help it?

00:25:09.340 --> 00:25:12.480 align:middle line:84%
Maybe they teach
us it's not CO2.

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:13.962 align:middle line:90%
It's some seem different.

00:25:13.962 --> 00:25:15.170 align:middle line:90%
You have to fight against it.

00:25:15.170 --> 00:25:25.050 align:middle line:90%


00:25:25.050 --> 00:25:29.190 align:middle line:84%
40 years from now, I
was invited by NASA.

00:25:29.190 --> 00:25:31.150 align:middle line:90%
It was a secret speech.

00:25:31.150 --> 00:25:35.760 align:middle line:84%
Both parties agreed that
none would go to public.

00:25:35.760 --> 00:25:38.830 align:middle line:84%
All the high professors
in rocketry were there.

00:25:38.830 --> 00:25:41.410 align:middle line:10%
In that speech, I
shortly also speak

00:25:41.410 --> 00:25:44.033 align:middle line:10%
about the prophet Ezekiel
in the Old Testament.

00:25:44.033 --> 00:25:47.420 align:middle line:90%


00:25:47.420 --> 00:25:49.670 align:middle line:10%
Later, we were all sitting
together at dinner,

00:25:49.670 --> 00:25:51.710 align:middle line:10%
and then the chief
of the construction

00:25:51.710 --> 00:25:55.490 align:middle line:10%
of NASA at that time,
Mr. Josef Blumrich,

00:25:55.490 --> 00:25:56.490 align:middle line:10%
came to me at the table.

00:25:56.490 --> 00:26:00.020 align:middle line:10%
Said Erich, you are the
first person who brings me

00:26:00.020 --> 00:26:02.180 align:middle line:10%
to this prophet Ezekiel.

00:26:02.180 --> 00:26:03.650 align:middle line:90%
I never read of this.

00:26:03.650 --> 00:26:06.150 align:middle line:84%
I will read this
in the next weeks.

00:26:06.150 --> 00:26:06.980 align:middle line:90%
He did it.

00:26:06.980 --> 00:26:12.420 align:middle line:84%
He read Ezekiel, and
he became astonished,

00:26:12.420 --> 00:26:16.350 align:middle line:84%
and started to take
Ezekiel seriously.

00:26:16.350 --> 00:26:19.140 align:middle line:84%
Then two other NASA scientists
came to him-- to Blumrich,

00:26:19.140 --> 00:26:22.800 align:middle line:84%
and said what are you doing
with the Bible on your desk?

00:26:22.800 --> 00:26:25.800 align:middle line:84%
He said, look, there's a
prophet calling Ezekiel.

00:26:25.800 --> 00:26:27.900 align:middle line:84%
He describes a vehicle
which came down.

00:26:27.900 --> 00:26:31.560 align:middle line:84%
We can reconstruct,
recalculate, what this vehicle

00:26:31.560 --> 00:26:33.030 align:middle line:90%
must have looked like.

00:26:33.030 --> 00:26:37.660 align:middle line:84%
Slowly, piece by piece, they
took every phrase of Ezekiel

00:26:37.660 --> 00:26:40.650 align:middle line:84%
seriously, not just
a few examples,

00:26:40.650 --> 00:26:44.320 align:middle line:84%
and they reconstructed
the spaceship of Ezekiel.

00:26:44.320 --> 00:26:47.490 align:middle line:10%
Mr. Jo Blumrich, Chief of the
NASA Constructing Department,

00:26:47.490 --> 00:26:48.720 align:middle line:10%
came out with the book.

00:26:48.720 --> 00:26:52.050 align:middle line:10%
The English title was "The
Spaceship of Ezekiel."

00:26:52.050 --> 00:26:56.790 align:middle line:84%
In the foreword, he
confesses he started his work

00:26:56.790 --> 00:26:58.830 align:middle line:90%
against Erich von Daniken.

00:26:58.830 --> 00:27:02.880 align:middle line:84%
He wanted to disprove
this idea of Ezekiel,

00:27:02.880 --> 00:27:06.630 align:middle line:84%
but he found on the
contrary, was true,

00:27:06.630 --> 00:27:08.040 align:middle line:90%
and he was very happy with his.

00:27:08.040 --> 00:27:11.740 align:middle line:90%


00:27:11.740 --> 00:27:14.950 align:middle line:84%
Still today, there
are a lot of skeptics

00:27:14.950 --> 00:27:18.340 align:middle line:84%
who think whatever Erich von
Daniken writes is garbage,

00:27:18.340 --> 00:27:22.630 align:middle line:84%
is nonsense, and I love the
discussions with skeptics

00:27:22.630 --> 00:27:25.630 align:middle line:84%
because they lose anyhow
in all discussion.

00:27:25.630 --> 00:27:27.850 align:middle line:84%
And whenever I come
together with skeptics

00:27:27.850 --> 00:27:31.040 align:middle line:84%
who think I'm an
idiot, I ask them,

00:27:31.040 --> 00:27:33.200 align:middle line:84%
which book-- which of
your titles have you read.

00:27:33.200 --> 00:27:34.750 align:middle line:90%
They say none.

00:27:34.750 --> 00:27:35.770 align:middle line:90%
They read nothing.

00:27:35.770 --> 00:27:39.280 align:middle line:10%
They simply knew in
advance it's all nonsense.

00:27:39.280 --> 00:27:41.830 align:middle line:10%
Of course, I learned
from the skeptics too.

00:27:41.830 --> 00:27:44.890 align:middle line:10%
In many cases, the critics
were correct, and I had to say

00:27:44.890 --> 00:27:47.980 align:middle line:10%
oh, come on, this point
of view makes more sense

00:27:47.980 --> 00:27:52.000 align:middle line:10%
than my point of view, which
is normally the discussion.

00:27:52.000 --> 00:27:54.760 align:middle line:84%
But roughly, the
extraterrestrials

00:27:54.760 --> 00:27:57.010 align:middle line:84%
were here some
thousands of years ago.

00:27:57.010 --> 00:27:59.980 align:middle line:84%
Our ancestors at that time could
not understand what it was.

00:27:59.980 --> 00:28:02.260 align:middle line:90%
They called it the gods.

00:28:02.260 --> 00:28:06.400 align:middle line:84%
Roughly, this story I
can prove by indication.

00:28:06.400 --> 00:28:13.190 align:middle line:90%


00:28:13.190 --> 00:28:15.840 align:middle line:90%
There are no gods, in reality.

00:28:15.840 --> 00:28:18.020 align:middle line:84%
So it's all a
misunderstanding, but they

00:28:18.020 --> 00:28:21.290 align:middle line:90%
believed these are the gods.

00:28:21.290 --> 00:28:23.720 align:middle line:84%
That's why the
so-called gods entered

00:28:23.720 --> 00:28:27.140 align:middle line:84%
into the big religions,
the mythologies, legends,

00:28:27.140 --> 00:28:28.310 align:middle line:90%
et cetera.

00:28:28.310 --> 00:28:31.880 align:middle line:10%
It's all a misunderstanding.

00:28:31.880 --> 00:28:34.040 align:middle line:84%
Well, my life has
changed because I'm

00:28:34.040 --> 00:28:37.640 align:middle line:84%
an enthusiastic man, and
I'm a man full of curiosity.

00:28:37.640 --> 00:28:39.410 align:middle line:90%
I always have new questions.

00:28:39.410 --> 00:28:42.110 align:middle line:90%


00:28:42.110 --> 00:28:45.310 align:middle line:84%
I still have no idea where did
these extraterrestrials come

00:28:45.310 --> 00:28:50.470 align:middle line:84%
from, which solar system, how
far away, with what technology?

00:28:50.470 --> 00:28:53.160 align:middle line:90%


00:28:53.160 --> 00:28:54.610 align:middle line:90%
What was finally the purpose?

00:28:54.610 --> 00:28:59.300 align:middle line:10%
Why have they chosen to come to
our planet or our solar system?

00:28:59.300 --> 00:29:03.030 align:middle line:84%
There are still hundreds of
open questions, which I've tried

00:29:03.030 --> 00:29:04.330 align:middle line:90%
to come closer and closer.

00:29:04.330 --> 00:29:08.320 align:middle line:90%


00:29:08.320 --> 00:29:11.590 align:middle line:84%
I've found brilliant
indications to support

00:29:11.590 --> 00:29:13.600 align:middle line:84%
that extraterrestrials
were here,

00:29:13.600 --> 00:29:16.600 align:middle line:84%
but I never found
a conclusive proof.

00:29:16.600 --> 00:29:19.540 align:middle line:84%
Until today, I am
missing an object.

00:29:19.540 --> 00:29:22.390 align:middle line:84%
An object which is not
from this planet, which

00:29:22.390 --> 00:29:26.230 align:middle line:84%
I could present proudly with
the scientific community.

00:29:26.230 --> 00:29:28.240 align:middle line:84%
This object is not
from our planet.

00:29:28.240 --> 00:29:29.290 align:middle line:90%
So help me out.

00:29:29.290 --> 00:29:31.600 align:middle line:90%
What is the situation?

00:29:31.600 --> 00:29:35.320 align:middle line:84%
But I know such objects do
exist because they were here,

00:29:35.320 --> 00:29:37.330 align:middle line:84%
and we have descriptions,
for example.

00:29:37.330 --> 00:29:39.100 align:middle line:84%
In the Bible, we
have descriptions

00:29:39.100 --> 00:29:43.790 align:middle line:84%
of the Ark of the Covenant,
and the Ark of the Covenant

00:29:43.790 --> 00:29:47.480 align:middle line:90%
was not a human object.

00:29:47.480 --> 00:29:48.960 align:middle line:10%
It was an
extraterrestrial object.

00:29:48.960 --> 00:29:50.870 align:middle line:10%
So we know that some
of these objects

00:29:50.870 --> 00:29:52.830 align:middle line:10%
exist, but we have
never found them.

00:29:52.830 --> 00:29:56.520 align:middle line:90%


00:29:56.520 --> 00:29:58.920 align:middle line:84%
In many other fields,
I know nothing.

00:29:58.920 --> 00:30:02.580 align:middle line:84%
I am just a student, happy
to learn from the others.

00:30:02.580 --> 00:30:05.320 align:middle line:84%
But in my field, I
know quite a lot.

00:30:05.320 --> 00:30:08.280 align:middle line:84%
So I can debate, and
that makes me happy.

00:30:08.280 --> 00:30:11.290 align:middle line:84%
New paradigms, new
way of thinking,

00:30:11.290 --> 00:30:15.100 align:middle line:84%
a new way of curiosity, a
new way of question mark.

00:30:15.100 --> 00:30:16.620 align:middle line:84%
That's what I'm
bringing forward,

00:30:16.620 --> 00:30:18.870 align:middle line:84%
and I hope that
society continues.

00:30:18.870 --> 00:30:22.150 align:middle line:90%


00:30:22.150 --> 00:30:24.910 align:middle line:84%
In the meantime,
I hope some of us

00:30:24.910 --> 00:30:28.130 align:middle line:90%
have learned we are not alone.

00:30:28.130 --> 00:30:30.250 align:middle line:84%
There are other
societies out there.

00:30:30.250 --> 00:30:34.180 align:middle line:84%
We have learned to become
a little more humble.

00:30:34.180 --> 00:30:37.170 align:middle line:84%
We have learned that
space travel is possible,

00:30:37.170 --> 00:30:38.430 align:middle line:90%
even from star to star.

00:30:38.430 --> 00:30:42.800 align:middle line:90%


00:30:42.800 --> 00:30:47.480 align:middle line:10%
We have learned that it is
possible to change the cell--

00:30:47.480 --> 00:30:49.590 align:middle line:10%
the DNA in the cell.

00:30:49.590 --> 00:30:54.580 align:middle line:84%
So it is possible
to create something.

00:30:54.580 --> 00:30:57.720 align:middle line:84%
I am sure we are the
product of evolution.

00:30:57.720 --> 00:31:01.920 align:middle line:84%
We cannot deny evolution,
but there was always,

00:31:01.920 --> 00:31:05.550 align:middle line:84%
in the past thousands of years,
somebody who did something

00:31:05.550 --> 00:31:07.140 align:middle line:90%
in our evolution.

00:31:07.140 --> 00:31:09.990 align:middle line:84%
Extraterrestrials,
from time to time,

00:31:09.990 --> 00:31:12.790 align:middle line:84%
made a little changing
in our evolution.

00:31:12.790 --> 00:31:17.050 align:middle line:84%
So in the future, our genetics
are brilliant personalities.

00:31:17.050 --> 00:31:21.030 align:middle line:84%
They will find out
this in the genes.

00:31:21.030 --> 00:31:25.110 align:middle line:84%
Soon as we notice, we all
are part of evolution,

00:31:25.110 --> 00:31:26.760 align:middle line:90%
but not only.

00:31:26.760 --> 00:31:29.760 align:middle line:84%
We are a little part of
extraterrestrials too.

00:31:29.760 --> 00:31:31.265 align:middle line:90%
That's why we understand them.

00:31:31.265 --> 00:31:33.390 align:middle line:84%
That's why we will understand
each other very well.

00:31:33.390 --> 00:31:39.090 align:middle line:90%


00:31:39.090 --> 00:31:42.050 align:middle line:84%
So my latest book
in English language

00:31:42.050 --> 00:31:44.480 align:middle line:84%
is a sequel of
"Chariots of the Gods."

00:31:44.480 --> 00:31:46.670 align:middle line:84%
I continue with
"Chariots of the Gods."

00:31:46.670 --> 00:31:50.450 align:middle line:84%
I say what happened
in the past 50 years?

00:31:50.450 --> 00:31:53.070 align:middle line:84%
What happened and
where do we stand now?

00:31:53.070 --> 00:31:54.870 align:middle line:90%
And it comes close to it.

00:31:54.870 --> 00:31:57.380 align:middle line:10%
We are under observation.

00:31:57.380 --> 00:32:03.570 align:middle line:10%
We have some UFO case which
we should take for serious.

00:32:03.570 --> 00:32:06.030 align:middle line:84%
That's the content
of my new book.

00:32:06.030 --> 00:32:07.510 align:middle line:90%
Be prepared.

00:32:07.510 --> 00:32:10.980 align:middle line:10%
We are under observation,
and sooner or later, they

00:32:10.980 --> 00:32:12.540 align:middle line:10%
will show up again.

00:32:12.540 --> 00:32:17.360 align:middle line:84%
The title is "The
Gods Never Left Us."

00:32:17.360 --> 00:32:23.382 align:middle line:90%